INSERT INTO `books` VALUES (51,'One Piece','Eiichiro Oda',19.99,'One Piece, created by Eiichiro Oda, is a legendary manga series that follows the epic adventures of Monkey D. Luffy, a spirited young pirate with the ability to stretch like rubber after eating a mysterious Devil Fruit. Luffy dreams of becoming the Pirate King by finding the \"One Piece,\" a fabled treasure left behind by the legendary pirate Gol D. Roger. Alongside his diverse and loyal crew, the Straw Hat Pirates, Luffy embarks on thrilling journeys across dangerous seas and enigmatic islands, battling formidable enemies, uncovering hidden secrets, and forming deep bonds with allies. Renowned for its rich world-building, dynamic characters, and a perfect balance of humor, action, and emotional depth, One Piece is a masterpiece that explores themes of friendship, freedom, and the pursuit of dreams.','https://i.pinimg.com/236x/ae/2b/f8/ae2bf823ded6903e12fd2c92758c8083.jpg','[\"Fiction\", \"Adventure\"]'),(52,'Whispers of Grace','Evelyn Harper',25.99,'Evelyn Harper is a poignant and inspiring story of faith, resilience, and self-discovery. The narrative follows a young girl named Clara as she faces life’s trials in a world that often feels overwhelming. Struggling to find her place, she discovers the transformative power of prayer, which becomes her anchor in moments of despair. Guided by an unwavering belief in something greater than herself, Clara embarks on a journey to heal old wounds, embrace her inner strength, and uncover the beauty hidden within lifes challenges. With heartfelt prose and evocative storytelling, Evelyn Harper weaves a tale that resonates deeply with anyone seeking hope, comfort, or a renewed sense of purpose. Whispers of Grace is a celebration of faith’s ability to illuminate the darkest paths and remind us all that grace can be found even in the most unexpected places.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT03-BGU4Fb5AvC5wymoXneeJzgvW5m3AO37g&s.jpg','[\"Fiction\"]'),(53,'《无羁》 (Wú Jī)','Mo Xiang Tong Xiu',19.99,'The first volume of the fantasy novel series Mo Dao Zu Shi (Grandmaster of Demonic Cultivation), is written by Chinese author Mo Xiang Tong Xiu. The story is set in a richly crafted fantasy world of cultivation and follows Wei Wuxian, a mischievous and talented cultivator who once delved into forbidden practices. After his tragic downfall, he is resurrected years later in the body of a man despised by his clan and must navigate a world filled with intrigue, danger, and secrets. Alongside his enigmatic ally, Lan Wangji, Wei Wuxian uncovers hidden truths that bind the present to his tumultuous past. The novel, blending elements of action, mystery, and romance, is a xianxia (fantasy martial arts) story, a subgenre of Chinese speculative fiction that often features cultivation, immortals, and mythical beings. It also explores deeper themes of morality, loyalty, and redemption, making it a beloved work among fans worldwide.','https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1545384470i/43294134.jpg','[\"Action\", \"Mystery\", \"Romance\"]'),(54,'Elon Musk','Walter Isaacson',25.99,'An in-depth biography of one of the most influential and controversial innovators of our time. Based on exclusive access to Musk and interviews with those closest to him, Isaacson delves into the life of the enigmatic entrepreneur behind Tesla, SpaceX, Neuralink, and The Boring Company. The book explores Musks complex personality, his relentless drive to push technological boundaries, and his vision to revolutionize transportation, energy, and space exploration.\nFrom his tumultuous childhood in South Africa to his triumphs and challenges as a business leader, the biography paints a vivid picture of Musks genius, ambition, and the cost of his obsession with shaping the future. Walter Isaacson, renowned for his biographies of other iconic figures like Steve Jobs, offers a balanced and gripping portrait of a man whose ideas and actions are reshaping the world.','https://books.google.com.my/books/publisher/content?id=HjyvEAAAQBAJ&pg=PA1946&img=1&zoom=3&hl=en&bul=1&sig=ACfU3U1J-bEdZKXSO5pNd6kAH82MTzmhuw&w=1280.jpg','[\"Biography\"]'),(55,'Marvel Comics','Stan Lee',25.99,'Marvel Comics is a renowned American comic book publisher, known for creating some of the most iconic superheroes and compelling stories in popular culture. Founded in 1939, it introduced legendary characters like Spider-Man, Iron Man, the Hulk, Thor, Captain America, the X-Men, and the Avengers, who have become beloved figures worldwide. Marvels comics are celebrated for their rich storytelling, complex characters, and interconnected universe, which blends action, drama, and humor. Over the decades, Marvel has expanded its reach beyond comics, influencing movies, TV shows, video games, and merchandise, creating a vibrant and immersive world for fans of all ages. Its ability to explore themes of heroism, identity, and morality while reflecting societal issues has solidified Marvels legacy as a cultural powerhouse in entertainment.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRLR4U-m3eaKDvW8dGJ9XmqNfEkXVjHQdD2Lg&s.jpg','[\"Action\", \"Adventure\"]'),(56,'The Amazing Spider-Man','Stan Lee',19.99,'\"The Amazing Spider-Man\" is one of Marvel Comics most iconic and long-running superhero series, centered around Peter Parker, a teenage high school student who gains spider-like abilities after being bitten by a radioactive spider. As Spider-Man, Peter uses his newfound powers—such as superhuman strength, agility, and the ability to cling to walls—to fight crime and protect New York City from various villains. However, Peters life is constantly weighed down by personal struggles, including balancing his responsibilities as a superhero with his everyday life, his relationships, and his guilt over the death of his Uncle Ben, which serves as a pivotal moment in his journey. The series is known for its deep character development, blending superhero action with personal drama, and exploring themes such as responsibility, sacrifice, and identity. Spider-Mans rogues gallery, which includes iconic villains like the Green Goblin, Doctor Octopus, and Venom, adds depth to the story, challenging Peter both physically and emotionally. \"The Amazing Spider-Man\" remains one of Marvels most beloved and influential comic book series, with countless adaptations into movies, TV shows, and other media.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQPzQiH5Huk1gDplmXpxlxqUXXXCIgjXb1i8Q&s.jpg','[\"Action\", \"Adventure\"]'),(57,'My Hero Academia','Kohei Horikoshi',25.99,'\"My Hero Academia\" (Boku no Hero Academia) is a popular Japanese manga and anime series written and illustrated by Kohei Horikoshi. Set in a world where nearly everyone possesses a unique ability known as a \"Quirk,\" the story follows Izuku Midoriya, a boy born without a Quirk but who still dreams of becoming a great hero like his idol, All Might, the worlds symbol of peace. After a fateful encounter with All Might, Izuku inherits his mentors Quirk, \"One For All,\" and is granted the chance to attend U.A. High School, an elite institution for aspiring heroes. At U.A., Izuku and his classmates undergo rigorous training to master their abilities and face challenges that test their strength, resolve, and teamwork. Along the way, they encounter various villains, including the League of Villains, and confront moral dilemmas about justice, heroism, and the consequences of their actions.','https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRefNX7OTZxCUato6fZewyy9TsMD3kzt333aw&s.jpg','[\"Action\", \"Adventure\"]'),(58,'Spy x Family','Tatsuya Endo',19.99,'The story revolves around an unlikely family formed for the sake of espionage and political intrigue. The main character, Twilight, is a highly skilled spy who is tasked with infiltrating a prestigious school to monitor a political figure. In order to maintain his cover, he creates a fake family. To do so, he adopts a young girl, Anya, who unbeknownst to him is a telepath, and marries Yor, a woman who, in secret, is an assassin working for a foreign government. As the family navigates their daily lives, each member is unaware of the others true identities. Twilight, the father, is a spy; Yor, the mother, is an assassin; and Anya, the daughter, can read minds. Despite their hidden secrets, they form a bond and begin to care for each other as a real family.','https://dispatch.barnesandnoble.com/content/dam/ccr/boutique/manga/anime/02232024-update/img_8.jpg','[\"Comedy\", \"Action\"]'),(59,'Jujutsu Kaisen','Gege Akutami',36.50,'In Jujutsu Kaisen, all living beings emanate energy called Cursed Energy (呪力, Juryoku), which arises from negative emotions that naturally flow throughout the body. Ordinary people cannot control this flow in their bodies. As a result, they continually lose Cursed Energy, resulting in the birth of Curses (呪い, Noroi), a race of spiritual beings whose primary desire is to bring harm to humanity. These Curses are shown as gruesome monsters: onryō (vengeful spirit), yūrei (ghosts), and yōkai.','https://rukminim2.flixcart.com/image/832/832/xif0q/book/4/4/r/jujutsu-kaisen-vol-4-original-imahy5kghugbjkmt.jpeg?q=70&crop=false','[\"Action\", \"Horror\"]'),(62,'斗罗大陆','唐家三少',15.00,'唐门外门弟子唐三，因偷学内门绝学为唐门所不容，跳崖明志时却发现没有死，反而以另外一个身份来到了另一个世界，一个属于武魂的世界，名叫斗罗大陆。这里没有魔法，没有斗气，没有武术，却有神奇的武魂。这里的每个人，在自己六岁的时候，都会在武魂殿中令武魂觉醒。武魂有动物，有植物，有器物，武魂可以辅助人们的日常生活。而其中一些特别出色的武魂却可以用来修炼并进行战斗，这个职业，是斗罗大陆上最为强大也是最荣耀的职业——魂师!\n当唐门暗器来到斗罗大陆，当唐三武魂觉醒，他能否在这片武魂的世界再铸唐门的辉煌？他能否成为这个世界的主宰：神?','https://gw.alicdn.com/imgextra/O1CN01FZ4gLE1ht1RM74Ica_!!6000000004334-2-yinhe.png_468x468Q75.jpg_.webp','[\"adventure\"]'),(63,'Rich dad poor dad','Robert T. Kiyosaki, Sharon Lechter',49.99,'The story begins with the author as a young boy, observing the contrasting financial mindsets and behaviors of his own father, the \"poor dad,\" and a friend\'s father, the \"rich dad.\" The poor dad held a high position in education and emphasized the importance of academic success, job security, and living within one\'s means. The rich dad, a successful entrepreneur, believed in building assets, investing wisely, and acquiring financial knowledge. It describes how the rich dad teaches the author and his friend finance through practical lessons.\n\nThroughout the book, Kiyosaki shares anecdotes and conversations that he had with the rich dad, who guided him on various aspects of money, wealth creation, and financial independence. He learns valuable lessons about the difference between assets and liabilities, the power of financial education, and the importance of taking calculated risks. Kiyosaki emphasizes the significance of acquiring assets that generate income, such as real estate and businesses, as opposed to liabilities that drain money, such as excessive consumer debt and unnecessary expenses. He introduces concepts like the cash flow quadrant, which categorizes individuals as employees, self-employed, business owners, or investors, highlighting the advantages and disadvantages of each quadrant.','https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/b/b9/Rich_Dad_Poor_Dad.jpg','[\"finance\"]'),(64,'西游记','吴承恩',69.99,'《西游记》中国古典四大名著之一，是中国古代一部浪漫主义长篇神魔小说，作者吴承恩，成书于16世纪明朝中叶，主要描写了唐僧、孙悟空、猪悟能、沙悟净师徒四人去西天取经，历经九九八十一难最后终于取得真经的故事。《西游记》自问世以来在中国乃至世界各地广为流传，被翻译成多种语言。书中孙悟空这个形象，以其鲜明的个性特征，在中国文学史上立起了一座不朽的艺术丰碑。《西游记》不仅内容极其丰富，故事情节完整严谨，而且人物塑造鲜活、丰满，想象多姿多彩，语言也朴实通达。更为重要的是，《西游记》在思想境界和艺术境界上都达到了前所未有的高度，可谓集大成者。\n\n内容分为三大部分：第一部分（一到七回）介绍孙悟空的神通广大，大闹天宫；第二部分（八到十二回）叙三藏取经的缘由；第三部分（十三到一百回）是全书故事的主体，写悟空等降伏妖魔，最终到达西天取回真经。','https://www.findingmoonbookstore.com/cdn/shop/products/608c15b2af5d22bedac1b7ce60b9fbe5_1200x1200.jpg?v=1646327242','[\"adventure\"]');
